Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
  worms.model.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Food, Projectile, Worm
public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class collecting the typical characteristics shared by game objects.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Emil Loevbak, Victor Le Pochat
